{"tid":2178936,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"俄羅斯釋出60年前核爆片段","createTime":"2020-08-28T18:00:32.000Z","updateTime":"2020-08-28T19:43:52.000Z","uid":270889,"like":4,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":15,"replies":[{"pid":"d981a48f8b80c46a605caab20cdad989852ed569","tid":2178936,"uid":270889,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-08-28T18:00:32.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/abomb.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/abomb.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/abomb.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/abomb.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n舊蘑菇雲 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/shocking.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/shocking.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/shocking.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n唔知呢個時候放出黎仲有無咩政治意味 <br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://twitter.com/Reuters/status/1299403875103825920?s=20\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Ftwitter.com%2FReuters%2Fstatus%2F1299403875103825920%3Fs%3D20&d=7GjM3WQHKJNqnWTuO28XyMo9o6IkP5%2Bxjkbf63jgWy4%3D&h=381effb7\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Ftwitter.com%2FReuters%2Fstatus%2F1299403875103825920%3Fs%3D20&h=bc07b2fe\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://twitter.com/Reuters/status/1299403875103825920?s=20</a><br />\n<br />\nRussia has released previously classified footage of <span class=\"red\">the world&rsquo;s largest nuclear explosion</span>, caused when the Soviet Union detonated the so-called Tsar Bomba almost 60 years ago.<br />\n<br />\nThe hydrogen bomb, which carried the force of 50 million tons of conventional explosives, was detonated in a test in October 1961, 4,000 metres over the remote Novaya Zemlya archipelago above the Arctic Circle.<br />\n<br />\nThe footage shows an immense fireball and a 60-km high mushroom cloud rising after the explosion lit up the sky. The views were captured from several angles by cameras installed on the ground and on board two Soviet aircraft.<br />\n<br />\n&ldquo;The testing of an exceptionally powerful hydrogen load ... confirmed that the Soviet Union is in possession of a thermo-nuclear weapon with power of 50 megatons, 100 megatons and more,&rdquo; a narrator tells the audience.<br />\n<br />\nThe documentary was published online for the first time by Russian state nuclear agency Rosatom last week as part of events <span class=\"red\">to mark 75th anniversary of Russia&rsquo;s atomic industry</span>.<br />\n<br />\nDeveloped between 1956 and 1961 as the Soviet Union engaged in a nuclear arms race with the United States, the Tsar Bomba - the King of Bombs - was the largest hydrogen bomb ever and was claimed to be 3,300 times as destructive as the weapon that levelled Hiroshima."},{"pid":"ebb37f1d6595e01a569b442bb4f332e30961559f","tid":2178936,"uid":325243,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-08-28T18:05:13.000Z","msg":"好似早十幾年都有"},{"pid":"50adaa9f93ea6192d0aab40d3eabb3bd1e142065","tid":2178936,"uid":39092,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-08-28T18:05:23.000Z","msg":"沙王炸彈梗係勁<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/touch.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n呢粒已經係減弱左一半"},{"pid":"2755619b6d77097566bb1067d1f0c3fd9a168a77","tid":2178936,"uid":11067,"like":16,"dislike":1,"score":15,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2020-08-28T18:10:25.000Z","msg":"痴撚線60年前嘅片 仲清過某啲手機流出嘅自拍片<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/touch.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"51a83f4e839ec8724bfc22057ba16556bc662c97","tid":2178936,"uid":174502,"like":5,"dislike":2,"score":3,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-08-28T18:12:17.000Z","msg":"放粒係北京喇"},{"pid":"f835a9bb69b04b35e64aab53f500117c5e43126a","tid":2178936,"uid":270889,"like":5,"dislike":1,"score":4,"quote":{"pid":"2755619b6d77097566bb1067d1f0c3fd9a168a77","tid":2178936,"uid":11067,"like":16,"dislike":1,"score":15,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2020-08-28T18:10:25.000Z","msg":"痴撚線60年前嘅片 仲清過某啲手機流出嘅自拍片<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/t